      %h2 About Bit Parrot
      %p This application was created because I found myself spending too much time tracking information about development things I needed to be on top of (meetups, blogs, tweets, and things like that). I also wanted to find information specific to my city. I also like building apps in Ruby on Rails. Rather than me manually tracking all of this I created an app to do it for me. You are welcome to use it as well.
      %p In the future I plan to create an email that sends out information gathered by the app, so you don't need to go to this site for information. Sign up for that here if you would like to keep updated when that is available, and tell us your city and other interests so we can keep those in mind as we build more features.
